Process Groups

Source: R/groupers.R
process_groups.Rd

Process Groups

Usage

process_groups(x)

Arguments

x

<list> of character vectors

Value

<list> of character vectors

Examples

random_hcpcs(10) |>
   split_lengths() |>
   remove_redundant() |>
   split_first() |>
   process_groups()
